org.cxio.core

Class CxReader

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cxio.core.AbstractCxReader
      • org.cxio.core.CxReader

  • public final class CxReader
extends AbstractCxReader
    This class is used to read aspect fragments (lists of aspect elements) from a input stream.
